      },
      "date": "2014-05-23 12:29:12.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nWRT the failures that are being seeing on the Onyx cluster, it occurred to me that in lbuild you will need to arrange for the zfs RPM to be unpacked with \"rpm2cpio | cpio\" in addition to the existing unpacking of the zfs-devel RPM.\n\nThis is because zfs-devel only contains unversioned library symlinks pointing at the libraries that are installed with the zfs RPM.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
